    "solution": "<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 1\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq415m/df20c071-6320-47d4-b91e-ea3bff56c72f/55529c90-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq415n.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq415m/df20c071-6320-47d4-b91e-ea3bff56c72f/55529c90-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq415n.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 2\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq4256/b4a38db2-7ebb-41f3-af94-973f41be2110/561613a0-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq4257.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq4256/b4a38db2-7ebb-41f3-af94-973f41be2110/561613a0-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq4257.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 3\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq42x4/0c735d0e-1700-4f7f-9217-c05df5f9c952/56af9480-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq42x5.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq42x4/0c735d0e-1700-4f7f-9217-c05df5f9c952/56af9480-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq42x5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 4\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq43ol/a206c8df-215f-4a25-8539-fe8cf4d3dfd3/57467d50-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq43om.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq43ol/a206c8df-215f-4a25-8539-fe8cf4d3dfd3/57467d50-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq43om.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p>Hence, 4 compounds does not follow octet rule for sulphur.</p><div></div>\n\n<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 5\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq44fv/87634da9-81b4-462b-a19b-c5f645cb805b/57dc54b0-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq44fw.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq44fv/87634da9-81b4-462b-a19b-c5f645cb805b/57dc54b0-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq44fw.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 6\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq458i/4c13b9e7-9631-4eb2-a5c3-a2755521ff59/5879a620-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq458j.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq458i/4c13b9e7-9631-4eb2-a5c3-a2755521ff59/5879a620-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq458j.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 7\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq45u7/831ffc9e-f060-487a-b1b8-c8a79a84aa11/58f0f900-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq45u8.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq45u7/831ffc9e-f060-487a-b1b8-c8a79a84aa11/58f0f900-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq45u8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Chemical Bonding & Molecular Structure Question 7 English Explanation 8\" src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobq46so/93a29069-7762-47a4-91c2-f00c0f7dcd3b/59ae2e80-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq46sp.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobq46so/93a29069-7762-47a4-91c2-f00c0f7dcd3b/59ae2e80-3f35-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobq46sp.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\">$$ \\text { Only } 1 \\text { set has all molecules with one Ip. } $$<p></p>",
